  <brief_title>DARE: Diabetes in cArdiac REhabilitation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Strict Glycemic Control on Improvement of Exercise Capacities (VO2 Peak, Peak Workload After Cardiac Rehabilitation, in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus With Coronary Artery Disease.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
